node.text: Yes definitely!!! 😢😢😢 miss this burger too 😰😰
@mysweetlittletooth 😊 hopefully it’s possible to dine out again soon!

Lunch today: Shake Shack + Yomie Yogurt 😍

Was disappointed to learn that dining in at food and beverage outlets will continue to be disallowed in reopening “Phase 1” from 02 June.

But I guess this is necessary to stay safe and overcome COVID-19.

Do you miss dining in at restaurants too?
More than dining in, we miss meeting friends
